- Continuist position: All traditions involve reconstruction and selection (4 papers)
- Nationalist instrumentalization: Traditions manipulated for political identity construction (5 papers)
- Legitimacy crisis: Invented traditions vulnerable to breakdown when exposed (2 papers)
